text: Joshua Gross Santana (born in 13 May 1993) is a football player who currently plays for the Hendrik-Ido-Ambacht-side ASWH and on the Aruban national team.https://hendrik-ido-ambacht.dekombinatie.nl/nieuws/algemeen/579852/josh- gross-santana-geniet-van-aswh- ==International career== Gross debuted on 9 September 2018 in a match against Bermuda in a 3-1 victory in the qualifying rounds of the CONCACAF Nations League. On 22 March 2019, Gross scored his first goal, but suffered a 3-2 defeat against St. Lucia. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Aruba international footballers Category:Eerste Klasse players Category:Hoofdklasse players Category:Derde Divisie players Category:Aruban footballers Category:ASWH players Category:Association football midfielders
